Unit Converter Pro : app for unit of measurement conversions, has the vast majority of them, but if one is in need can just create new UoM easily and whole new categories
                     like specific energy content, etc 
                     link: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.unitconverterpro.ucplite&hl=en&gl=US
                     
getdata graph digitizer: app for getting numerical data from plots, graphs, etc. easy to use and fairly useful if one needs to get the plotted data in a paper.
                     link: http://getdata-graph-digitizer.com/
                     
DWSIM: free simulation software for simulating plants, unit operation (both rigorously and not) and tons of other stuff
                     link: https://sourceforge.net/projects/dwsim/
                     
                     
